###创建任务
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Review Spring Boot",
  "description": "Understand controller and repository",
  "deadline": "2026-07-25"
}

###查看所有任务
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks

###查看已完成任务
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks?status=completed

###查看未完成任务
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks?status=pending

###查看指定任务
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1

###查看本周完成数量
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/stats/weekly

###修改任务
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Review Spring Boot CRUD",
  "description": "Finish task update and delete APIs",
  "deadline": "2026-07-28"
}

### 标记任务完成
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/2/complete

###删除任务
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1
